main event: A dark, elliptical UFO was observed hovering in the sky over Davenport, Iowa, on June 6, 1968, with reports from multiple witnesses.
interesting points: The object was visible for approximately 20 minutes before it rapidly accelerated and disappeared from view., The witness reported the object moving in a zig-zag pattern without making any noise., The size of the UFO was estimated to be about 20-25 feet in diameter., Two other witnesses were present at the sighting, corroborating the observations., The case remains classified as unidentified after multiple investigations.
sighted object: a dark, elliptical or oval-shaped object
witness description: Mr. Gordon S. Roesbeke, age 75, and two other witnesses
